OL,5, TV chef Dave Myers has revealed he is  
OL,6, undergoing chemotherapy after receiving
OL,7, a cancer diagnosis.                    
OL,9,FThe 64-year-old is best-known as one   
OL,10,Fhalf of the celebrity cooking duo the  
OL,11,FHairy Bikers, alongside Si King.       
OL,13,FSpeaking on their Agony Uncles podcast,
OL,14,FMyers told his friend and fellow chef  
OL,15,Fhe would be taking a break from filming
OL,16,Fand certain public events.             
OL,18,F"Anyway Kingy, I've got to come clean  
OL,19,Fnow, I haven't been too well recently,"
OL,20,Fhe revealed.                           
